# The Agent SDK declares a peer on zod 4, but the contract layer (driver/contracts.ts)
# is written against zod 3 and the SDK is not yet imported (the invokeSubagent seam
# in driver/orchestrator.ts is still stubbed). Allow the install to proceed; reconcile
# the zod major when the SDK is actually wired — verify its signature against current
# docs at that point (ARCHITECTURE.md §2).
legacy-peer-deps=true
